'''Annoo-dat''' was the name used by two separate [[Species/Legends|species]] who lived as a single culture on [[Annoo (Gelefil)|Annoo]], an [[Agriworld/Legends|agriworld]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]].

The [[Annoo-dat Prime|original Annoo-dat]] were four-eyed reptiles indigenous to the original planet [[Annoo (original)|Annoo]]. They abandoned their homeworld and conquered Gelefil, and the [[Annoo-dat Blue|Ret]] natives of that world. Afterward, the Ret called themselves Annoo-dat as well, and Gelefil's name was changed to Annoo. [[Xenobiologist/Legends|Xenobiologists]] called the original Annoo-dat "Annoo-dat Prime", and called the Ret [[Annoo-dat Blue]]. The two Annoo-dat peoples had a unified culture, however, and did not pay attention to such distinctions.

